nd technology company it provides tools and solutions for talent customer and operations management the firm operates through the following segments ceb and ceb talent assessment the ceb segment includes comprehensive data analysis research advisory services customized personnel assessment tools and services the ceb talent assessment segment includes the shl product and services of cloudbased solutions for talent assessment development strategy analytics decision support and professional services that support those solutions enabling client access to data analytics insights for assessing managing employees and applicants the company was founded by david g bradley in  and is headquartered in arlington va senior directorglobal planning  analysis prior headstrong group inc headstrong group inc provides management consulting services the company is headquartered in fairfax va senior managerfinance prior bristolmyers squibb company bristolmyers squibb company our company has a strong legacy of innovation that began in new york in  when edward r squibb md founded a pharmaceutical company in brooklyn and in 7 when two friends william mclaren bristol and john ripley myers purchased a struggling drug manufacturing firm in clinton together they laid the foundation for our company today — a global biopharma leader that continues this legacy of innovation accountant prior friedman llp friedman llp provides accounting services it offers audit and assurance human resources solutions international services transaction advisory services forensic litigation and valuation services and pension administration services the firm serves the automotive communications fashion financial services government healthcare life sciences manufacturing notforprofit professional services real estate and technology industries the company was founded in  and is headquartered in new york ny public holdings restricted data only for relsci professional users start my free trial ➤ see more other affiliatio